<br />Do any of you guys know if it would do any damage if I "deinterlace" the graphics (usually, the first and the second bit come in different planes - <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_pattern_tables" class="postlink">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_pattern_tables</a>)? I think it would be easier to work this way.</div>

